org.apache.flink.table.store.table

Interface Table

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataTable, FileStoreTable, InnerTable, ReadonlyTable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFileStoreTable, AppendOnlyFileStoreTable, AuditLogTable, BucketsTable, ChangelogValueCountFileStoreTable, ChangelogWithKeyFileStoreTable, FilesTable, OptionsTable, SchemasTable, SnapshotsTable

    @Experimental
public interface Table
extends Serializable
    A table provides basic abstraction for table type and table scan and table read.

    0.4.0
